item.title: CVE-2019-9141|2024-09-16T18:03:06.693Z -- imgtech%20co%2Cltd -- zinsvx.dll%20activex%20control
item.description: ZInsVX.dll ActiveX Control 2018.02 and earlier in Zoneplayer contains a vulnerability that could allow remote attackers to execute arbitrary files by setting the arguments to the ActiveX method. This can be leveraged for remote code execution.
